name: Rio Matanza Riachuelo, Barrio de La Boca, CABA, Argentina - 06/19/2016
description:
In 2016, I was visiting my sister, who was studying at the UBA in Buenos Aires. Someday she and a friend took me on a visit to the "La Boca" district, which is the place where tango was born, and it also has one of the most famous soccer stadia: "La Bombonera" the home of the team "Boca Jrs.". If you are planning a visit, you have to try a choripan from the grills around the stadium.

I took this photo at the end of the long walk around the streets while we were waiting for the bus back home.
